        "a": "The logger is the MVP. Ship the ability to pick an exercise from a licensed library or one built-in template, log sets as weight times reps with last session's numbers shown inline, an auto rest timer and plate math on the log screen, and a simple history view with a personal record and basic volume chart. Cut adaptive AI programming, social features, wearable fusion, and camera work from v1."
