        "q": "What are the must-have features of a yoga app?",
        "a": "A filtered class library (by style, level, duration, focus, and teacher), a reliable follow-along video or audio player with pose cues and breath pacing, timed flows and sequences, structured programs or challenges with streaks, and a pose reference. Offline downloads and background audio are close behind because people practice without signal."
